        "name": "qrcode_generate_qr",
        "description": "Generates a QR code PNG image from text or URL using the qrserver.com API. Params: data — text or URL to encode; size — image width/height in pixels (default 300); fill_hex — QR module color as hex without # (default 000000); back_hex — background color as hex without # (default FFFFFF); ecl — error correction level L/M/Q/H (default M). Returns JSON string with output_type image_base64 and PNG encoded as base64.",
        "cspl": "fython",
